## KNOWN DEPRECATIONS

The following patterns exist in the iOS codebase but are explicitly deprecated.
Do NOT port them to Android:

| Deprecated | Replacement | File |
|---|---|---|
| Global `creditBalanceCents: Int` | `creditBalanceByClubID: [UUID: Int]` | `system_contracts.me В§3` |
| `use_credits` RPC via PostgREST | Direct PATCH on `player_credits` | `system_contracts.me В§3` |
| `issue_cancellation_credit` RPC via PostgREST | Direct PATCH/INSERT on `player_credits` | `system_contracts.me В§3` |
| `bookadink-preset://` URL scheme | Not used | `client_guardrails.me В§1` |
| `tournament` as skill_level value | Use `advanced` | `data_contracts.me В§3` |
| Global platform subscription billing via Google Play | Stripe subscriptions only | `platform_adaptation.me В§10` |
